added.description: After suffering trauma from being the dunk-ee in a dunking booth, Prohyas has trouble getting through the dunk based traps in Man Fish's lair.

added.title: Helping Cattus Help
added.description: The search for a mythical creature gets rather metaphysical when the equally elusive Cattus' assists the mission.

added.title: El Silencio
added.description: ¿Acaso Gumball y Darwin se quedaron sin cosas que decirse el uno al otro?
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.title: El Deseo
added.description: Gumball y Darwin creen que convirtieron a la señorita Simian en un almohadón para el cuello.
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.title: El Agente
added.description: En una misión escolar super secreta, Gumball se comporta como cierto sofisticado agente secreto británico.
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.title: El Desastre
added.description: Gumball y Darwin cuidan y luego pierden a la hermanita de Penny.
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.title: La Revuelta
added.description: Darwin siente pena por los objetos del hogar en Elmore y los motiva a alzarse.
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.title: Los Mejores Amigos
added.description: Cuando el mejor amigo de Gumball regresa a la ciudad, Darwin se pone celoso.
added.originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

added.description: Los sueños de los Osos bebés se hacen realidad cuando encuentran un billete de 100 dólares. Pero cuando no soportan la idea de gastarlo, se dan cuenta de lo difícil que es desprenderse.

added.title: Conejos
added.description: Los Osos bebés conocen a un grupo de conejos indefensos. Cuando descubren que los conejos viven aterrados de unos cuervos despiadados, los Osos deciden convertirse en héroes y ayudarlos.

added.title: Panda dos
added.description: Panda bebé es un sujeto de estudio que vive feliz en un ambiente aislado. Pero cuando llega Panda 2, un nuevo amigo, su visión del mundo se sacude, lo cual lo lanza a una gran aventura.

added.title: Batalla Laser
added.description: Los Osos bebé se inscriben en un juego láser de tiro, con la esperanza de ganar un poco de helado. Pero la ronda de tiros resulta más una zona de guerra que un juego.

added.title: Los Osos no pueden saltar
added.description: Para ganar una pizza, los Osos bebé jugan baloncesto contra una pandilla variada de niños.

added.title: Dolores del crecimiento
added.description: Perricornio está cansado de que Unikitty siempre lo ayude y ya no quiere ser el hermano pequeño, así que usa un poco del dulce de crecimiento de la Dra. Fox para ser más grande que Unikitty.

added.title: Videos musicales
added.description: Unikitty conduce un programa de videos musicales, presentando a la eufórica audiencia los cuatro mejores videos musicales del Unireino protagonizados por nuestros personajes favoritos.

added.title: Un dia nevado
added.description: Cuando una tormenta de nieve llega a la ciudad, Master Frown trata de arruinar la diversión de todos fingiendo ser un muñeco de nieve mágico. Pero cuando se congela por dentro, Master Frown debe preocuparse menos por arruinar la diversión de todos y más por no convertirse en un témpano malhumorado, imientras se ve obligado a experimentar la alegría de la temporada navideña!

added.title: El pollo maniaco
added.description: Después de hacerse amigo de un pollo con mala actitud en un zoológico de contacto, este lo sigue de regreso a la escuela. Él defiende la mala conducta del ave hasta que ya no puede seguir haciéndolo.

added.title: La cita
added.description: Cuando Chef está feliz ordena pizza para los niños. Esto le da a Owen & Jude la idea de crear una falsa admiradora secreta para Chef.

added.title: Conquistando torres
added.description: Duncan, Leshawna y Jude quieren una pieza de esquina del pastel de cumpleaños de Izzy, pero, ¿están preparados para hacer cualquier cosa por conseguir uno?

added.title: Y todos nos llevamos bien
added.description: Owen y Beth tratan de salvar un hormiguero que Courtney y Leshawna quieren destruir.

added.title: Duo Espinoso
added.description: Después de dejar Pequeña Escuela Madre, Steven ha encontrado un nuevo pasatiempo: las plantas.

added.title: Show de momias
added.description: Duncan sale en una misión para espantar a Courtney durante una excursión al museo.

added.title: El Camino
added.description: iEste episodio transcurre cuando los Osos son cachorritos! Los tres Osos, en su viaje por el desierto, se topan con un depósito gigante. Los Osos tratan de convertir este paraíso repleto de cajas en su hogar.

added.title: Tienda De Mascotas
added.description: En este episodio sobre los primeros años de vida de los Osos, se cuenta la historia del lugar en el que vivieron alguna vez cuando eran bebés. Luego de un altercado con el equipo que filmaba un video absolutamente conmovedor de adopción de animales, los Osos por poco aprovechan la oportunidad de encontrar hogares alejados uno del otro.

added.title: El chico del 3030
added.description: Los niños conocen a un misterioso niño del futuro y tratan de ayudarlo a completar su misión.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Club de Lectura Secreto
added.description: Kelsey crea un club de lectura supersecreto para introducir a Craig y JP en las alegrías de la lectura.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Cena en el Arroyo
added.description: Bernard queda a cargo de sus hermanos durante la noche, así que Craig se va a buscar su propia cena en el Arroyo.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Magia Tragica
added.description: Cuando Richard monta un espectáculo de magia amateur, la Dra. Fox se obsesiona por descubrir cómo se hacen esos trucos que desafían la ciencia. Pero mientras se propone usar todo su intelecto para encontrar formas experimentales de hacer los trucos que vio en la fiesta del cachorro, ¿acaso arruinará accidentalmente el asombro de la magia?

added.title: Senor Casero
added.description: El propietario amenazó a Master Frown y a Brock con desalojarlos a menos que arreglen el daño que le hicieron a su apartamento. Preocupado, Brock invita a Unikitty y a la pandilla para que los ayuden. En lugar de hacer lo que los chicos quieren en su casa, Unikitty procede a hacer lo que ella quiere. Al darse cuenta de su error, devuelve el apartamento a su antiguo estado asqueroso, pero ahora Frown y Brock están en peligro de desalojo de nuevo. Deben aliarse a Unikitty y la banda para luchar contra el malvado casero y salvar su hogar.

added.title: El Desfile
added.description: Unikitty planea un desfile para celebrar lo que cada uno tiene de único, idonde cada uno diseñará sus propias carrozas personalizadas! Pero Master Frown planea arruinar el desfile con una carroza súper deprimente. El desfile se convierte en un duelo intenso (y de una lentitud divertidísima) de coche contra carroza mientras Unikitty y los demás intentan derribar a Master Frown! ¿Le pondrá un freno Unikitty al complot a baja velocidad de Frown?

added.title: Lista de Traviesos
added.description: Es Nochebuena y Brock está emocionado por la visita de Santa Claus. Mientras se prepara para que Master Frown le lea un cuento para dormir, Unikitty y la banda irrumpen en su casa. Están ahí para evitar que Master Frown arruine más Navidades. Frown se declara inocente, pero Unikitty y la banda cuentan las historias de las Navidades pasadas que ya arruinó. ¿Frown probará su inocencia o se pondrá a la cabeza de la lista de los traviesos?

added.title: Bati-Kitty
added.description: La banda está lavando ropa en la lavandería local, cuando Unikitty encuentra el uniforme de Batman mezclado con su ropa. Embriagada al ver lo genial que es el disfraz, Unikitty adopta la personalidad de Batman y comienza a luchar contra el crimen. Cuando accidentalmente hace que Master Frown intensifique su actividad delictiva, Unikitty necesitará la ayuda de sus amigos, vestidos todos como Robin, para detenerlo.

added.title: Mision solitaria
added.description: Craig debe atender una "emergencia", dejando a Kelsey sola en el Tronco.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Superado
added.description: Cuando Rufus y Reg llegan para engañar al pueblo, el sheriff Mao Mao les enseña una lección sobre la justicia.

added.title: Duele Crecer
added.description: Steven va al médico por primera vez.

added.title: Lucha de Pulgares
added.description: El trío decide concursar en la competencia anual de Lucha de Pulgares, pero una sorpresa obliga a Mao Mao a lidiar con algo impensado… la derrota.

added.title: En Suenos
added.description: Los sueños de Steven comienzan a transmitirse en el televisor de su dormitorio.

added.title: La Aventura de la Moto de Mao Mao
added.description: Cuando Mao Mao subestima por igual a sus enemigos y a sus amigos, por poco le cuesta el reino entero.

added.title: Conquista de Popularidad
added.description: Cuando Mao Mao descubre que no es tan popular como Colosal y Adorabat, sus amigos deciden reinventarlo en forma de un héroe más amable y tierno.

added.title: Juntos por Siempre
added.description: Connie tiene una visión muy clara de su futuro, y Steven quiere asegurarse de ser parte de esa visión.

added.title: El es el Sheriff
added.description: iEl trío lucha por deshacerse del Rey cuando los acompaña como nuevo ayudante del sheriff por un día!

added.title: Bismuto Casual
added.description: Perla invita a Bismuto a la pista de patinaje para darle una lección sobre cómo forjar relaciones humanas.

added.title: Blankie
added.description: It's bedtime and Bing's getting ready for bed. But what will he do when his blankie gets wet in the toilet?

added.title: Get Lost Loula
added.description: Let's play Hide and Seek! Pocoyo is the seeker and is brilliant at it - but only thanks to Loula. When Loula gets all the praise for being a super-seeker, Pocoyo is jealous. He throws a ball very far away to make Loula run off and chase it. His friends think it was a nasty thing to do and so Pocoyo feels bad and decides he must now find Loula. They follow her footprints but she's gone really far and they just can't find her anywhere. Finally at an island in the sea they despair: they think she's gone forever. But we can already see that Loula is safe and sound. Everyone is reunited and Pocoyo can celebrate being a super-seeker too, after all.

added.title: Caillou and the Big Slide/Caillou the Sailor/Caillou and the Creepy Crawlies
added.description: The playschool is going swimming, and it's Caillou's very first time on a water slide./Mommy and Daddy are going out to a party and Caillou is excited to hear that Grandpa is coming to babysit./Rosie doesn't like bugs - she thinks they're icky!

added.title: Wrong!
added.description: On an orchard outing, picking bushels of fresh apples for Granny's home-baked pies, the Baby Looney Tunes encounter Melissa, who is in a mood to tell everyone that her method of apple picking is the only way.

added.title: Win, Lose or Daffy
added.description: A day playing miniature golf is fun for everyone but Baby Daffy, who believes he must beat everyone else at the game. At the end of the day, all but Daffy are having a good time regardless of how they scored.

removed.title: Swing Set Jet Set
removed.description: Axel and the team battle Princess SugarSalt for possession of Bearbarian's hammer, traded to her by one of their own - Galileo!

removed.title: My Enemy, My Friend
removed.description: The Ice Emperor's terrible Ice Dragon strikes again, laying waste to the Ice Fisher's village, forcing the ninja to go after Lloyd…

removed.title: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs/Mizzen in Action
removed.description: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs: The girls must literally work as one to try and stop Mojo from destroying Townsville./Mizzen in Action: Captain Crack McGraigen and his crew are tossed forward in time where discover the chemical X that marks the spot and it is up to the girls and Professor to send the super-charged pirates back to their own time.

removed.title: ThunderDogs
removed.description: The Thundercats agree to foster a demonic puppy from the Astral Plane until they can find it the perfect owner. But could the perfect owner be their worst enemy? Their worst enemy is Mumm-Ra in case you forgot!

removed.title: Side Kicked
removed.description: Zoe builds her own battle suit in hopes of joining Axel's team. The only problem? She can't shrink! Hijinks ensue as a full-sized Zoe tries to assist Axel & co. in a battle against Pyrant and his army of mind-control drones.

removed.title: Candy Is Dandy/Catastrophe
removed.description: Candy Is Dandy: When the Mayor gives the girls some candy in gratitude for saving the day, they become hooked on the stuff. They even make a deal with a local villain to commit crimes for treats./Catastrophe: A monster is frantically tearing up the town looking for his lost kitty. But in a city the size of Townsville, how can the girls find one lone cat?

removed.title: La Ultima Cambia Formas
removed.description: Akita cuenta la historia de "la Elección" y cómo es que ella y su hermano gemelo, Kataru, fueron al bosque para descubrir su forma animal.

removed.title: A Made Up Story
removed.description: Someone is defacing all the posters and statues of Townsville with make-up. Can the girls stop this makeover takeover or will they get the blush off?

removed.title: Cambiando Objetos
removed.description: Axel y el equipo luchan contra la Princesa SugarSalt por la posesión del martillo de Bearbarian, que le vendió uno de los suyos: iGalileo!

removed.title: #WhySoBlue
removed.description: Supergirl must rein in a reckless new hero, the Blue Beetle.

removed.title: Who's the Fake?!/Trouble Busters! 2
removed.description: With the reveal that Haavik is a shapeshifting Alien, the ABs start to get super-paranoid, realizing that ANYONE could be Haavik in disguise. The suspicion quickly turns inward, and the ABs are left wondering if they have an imposter among them!/ A kid brawler named Oliver has lost his Bakugan! This seems like a job for the Trouble Busters. The Awesome Brawlers help him chase down and try to catch the elusive Bakugan, who leads them on a wild goose chase through Los Volmos.

removed.title: #WarriorAndTheJester
removed.description: After accidentally destroying one of Babs' beloved, one-of-a-kind Batman keepsakes, Diana enlists the help of Harleen Quinzel in order to find a replacement in Gotham City.

removed.title: A Fragile Hope
removed.description: Having discovered the terrible truth of Zane's fate, Lloyd finds himself imprisoned and alone in the clutches of the Ice Emperor.

removed.title: Wizz-Ra
removed.description: The ThunderCats freak out when a spooky ghost dressed like a pharaoh appears in their mirrors! They quickly set about to getting rid of every reflective surface in their lair, because that ghost is scary and no one wants to talk to him!

removed.title: VIP Baby You Know Me
removed.description: Shag Rugg makes a VIP section in his family's Café to live his baller life style.

removed.title: Access Denied
removed.description: When Axel and the team try to figure out what Sarge Charge's secret weapon is, they get ejected from the house by his newly upgraded security system and must fight their way back inside before Madcap does.

removed.title: La Dinamica del Dinamo
removed.description: iAxel se encuentra en el centro de un desacuerdo entre Sarge y Masko sobre lo que es más importante en la batalla, el arma o el que lo maneja, después de que Dynamo une al trío!

removed.title: Ice Guys Finish Last
removed.description: Chef brings a souvenir iceberg home from a trip to the South Pole and Duncan finds a prehistoric surprise inside.

removed.title: The Last of the Formlings
removed.description: Akita tells the story of the "Choosing" and how she, and her twin brother, Kataru, went into the wilds to discover their animal forms.

removed.title: Companera Nueva
removed.description: Zoe construye su propio traje de batalla con la esperanza de unirse al equipo de Axel. ¿El único problema? Ella no puede encogerse! Se producen hijinks cuando una Zoe de tamaño completo intenta ayudar a Axel & co. en una batalla contra Pyrant y su ejército de drones de control mental.

removed.title: Corruption
removed.description: The story of Zane's arrival in the Never-Realm and how he fell under the sway of the villainous Vex.

removed.title: El ProtocoloKaiju
removed.description: De vuelta en la ciudad de Ninjago, Wu y Pixal intentan localizar el Reino del Jamás y liberan accidentalmente a una temida criatura del Reino de los Muertos.

removed.description: El terrible Dragón de Hielo del Emperador ataca de nuevo, arrasando la aldea de los Pescadores de Hielo, obligando a los ninjas a seguir los pasos de Lloyd.

removed.title: Patolli
removed.description: When Valentino's has a hot winning streak at an ancient board game, his beginner's luck gets the best of him until, he meets his match. Will he reign as champion or lose it all?

removed.title: #MotherKnowsBest
removed.description: Hippolyta visits town and Diana is desperate to win her approval. But when Hippolyta unexpectedly takes a shine to Kara, Diana must curb her envy before they all get hurt.

removed.title: Una Fragil Esperanza
removed.description: Después de descubrir la terrible verdad del destino de Zane, Lloyd se encuentra en el calabozo, en las garras del Emperador de Hielo.

removed.title: Corrupcion
removed.description: Conoceremos la historia de la llegada de Zane al Reino del Jamás y cómo cayó bajo el dominio del villano Vex.

removed.title: Cookie Trouble
removed.description: Tig and Seek face their most devious foe yet… a cookie scout.

removed.title: Attack of Thermometron 9000
removed.description: Axel must wrangle Galileo and Bobbie to shut down a rogue thermostat - improperly upgraded by Slobot - as it plunges the house into extreme hot and cold zones.

removed.title: #AcceptNoSubstitute
removed.description: Feeling smothered, Babs urges her retired dad, Commissioner Gordon, to get a hobby, but her advice backfires when the Commissioner becomes a substitute teacher at her school!

removed.title: Custody Battle/City of Nutsville
removed.description: Custody Battle: Mojo discovers the Rowdyruff Boys are back and is determined to show them that he is a more evil dad than Him./The City of Nutsville: The squirrels of Townsville are chirping mad! But when Bubbles loses her ability to speak a squirrel, the girls don't know how to calm the rodents down.

removed.title: The Kaiju Protocol
removed.description: Back in Ninjago City, Wu and Pixal attempt to locate the Never-Realm, and accidentally unleash a dreaded creature from the Departed Realm…

removed.title: The Dynamo Dynamic
removed.description: Axel finds himself at the center of a disagreement between Sarge and Masko over what's more important in battle - the weapon or the one who wields it - after Dynamo bonds the trio together!

removed.title: Quiche it Goodbye
removed.description: When an "evil conglomerate" is threatening to takeover Chef's favourite childhood restaurant, Owen rallies the kids to take them down.

removed.title: Acceso Denegado
removed.description: Cuando Axel y el equipo intentan descubrir cuál es el arma secreta de Sarge Charge, son expulsados ​​de la casa por su sistema de seguridad recientemente actualizado y deben abrirse camino antes de que Madcap lo haga.

removed.title: The Ring
removed.description: Tiggy and Prangle compete for Mrs. Grendelsons' heart.

removed.title: Mini Mongor
removed.description: The Thunderkittens unleash a demon who is powered by fear. Too bad he's small and not that scary.

A Storm's on the Way: Still upset that Ajit has given up his life as a phantom thief, Storm rolls out Hydranoid x Aquos and attacks! Ajit and Lia take off running through the maze as Storm gives chase.

removed.title: Tygra's Garden
removed.description: Tygra says he's done being a Thundercat after he gets engaged to a sentient flower. Now it's up to Lion-O to break up the wedding!

removed.title: Dusk Industries Under Attack/Taking Dan Back
removed.description: Dusk Industries Under Attack: "Bad Dan" has his taken his rampage to Dusk Industries and this time he has help spreading the chaos and destruction, he's joined by Sophie, McQ, Everett, Storm and Haavik! The Awesome Brawlers, with some help from Magnus, are determined to an end to this show of destruction and get their friend back!

removed.title: Plan-De-Monium
removed.description: Val has meticulously planned for the perfect day of activities with Isabella, but his rigid insistence on sticking to the itinerary make for a less than perfect experience.

removed.title: Eyesore a Sunset
removed.description: Art is subjective and Apple and Onion agree to let that get between them.

removed.title: Swampy Johnny
removed.description: The Thundercats invite a super cool swamp man into the Cat's Lair who is on the run from some scary looking aliens!

removed.title: #CruzControl
removed.description: Working toward her dream of making her school a better place, Jessica runs for class president. However, when her opponent, the corrupt Oswald Cobblepot, pulls ahead in the race using less-than-honest means, Jessica finds herself compromising the integrity of her honest campaign to beat him!

removed.title: Golden Bakugan Encounter/Ties of Gold
removed.description: Golden Bakugan Encounter: Dan and Shun, split up from the rest of Awesome Brawlers, are traveling in through the maze when they discover McQ. It turns out McQ is seeking a golden Bakugan. When the boys go in for a closer look, they are startled by an old friend, and together confront McQ./Ties of Gold: The now reunited Awesome Brawlers are once again confronted by Storm, McQ, Sophie and Everett, who are on the hunt for golden Bakugan. With tired Bakugan, the Awesome Brawlers will have to give it their all to defend against this evil.

removed.title: DC
removed.description: It's Wonder Woman's 80th birthday, so the Titans head to DC Headquarters for the party.

removed.title: Nightmare/Bad Dan
removed.description: Nightmare: Dan hasn't been sleeping well lately. No "sleep brawling" this time, but he's constantly tossing and turning. With "Bad Dan" causing all kinds of havoc and destruction, the rest of the Awesome Brawlers have no choice but to roll out to try to contain "Bad Dan".

removed.title: The Legend of the Library
removed.description: When the library is thrown into disarray, an ancient ghost is awoken.

removed.title: El Kabong's Kabong is Gone
removed.description: When El Kabong's guitar breaks, he must find a new instrument of justice.

removed.title: The Headsucker's Moxy/Equal Fights
removed.description: The Headsucker's Moxy: There's a mysterious villain in town who's sucking pertinent information from the brains of powerful people and committing crimes. How do the girls trap this sucker before his next victim is drained?/Equal Fights: When the girls try to catch a local female villain, she tells them that as women they've got to stick together. It's up to the women of Townsville to teach our heroines the true meaning of equality.

removed.title: Pepo The Pumpkinman
removed.description: A magic hat brings the Titans' pumpkinman to life, but they have to figure out how to keep Pepo from rotting.

removed.title: Ataque de Thermometron 9000
removed.description: Axel debe lidiar con Galileo y Bobbie para apagar un termostato deshonesto, que Slobot actualizó incorrectamente, ya que sumerge la casa en zonas extremadamente frías y calientes.

removed.title: Transylbabies
removed.description: A mission to babysit Snowmanpire babies in Transylbiria leads Vambre and Prohyas to attack the local monster townsfolk in misguided attempts to keep the Snowbabies safe.

removed.title: Don't Read the Comments
removed.description: An obsession with comments and criticisms about him on the Board of Opinions drives Prohyas nuts, affecting Warrior missions for the worse and raising Vambre's ire, I mean, concerns.

removed.description: The Warriors don't have a worthy adventure to use their impressive new skull-and-crossbones-emblazoned Bonehead Magisword until they are sent on a quest to battle a mighty slime beast in the Dungeon of Gelatinous Doom!

removed.description: When Vambre and Prohyas are hired for separate gigs, they end up having to battle each other to claim a rare Squideo from Lake Sprite in Galacton.

removed.title: Bad Heir Day
removed.description: Princess Zange's Autostyle Magisword is stolen and it's up to the Warriors to retrieve it so their royal leader can face her subjects without bad hair.

removed.title: Beat Your Greens/Down N' Dirty
removed.description: Beat Your Greens: When Broccoli Aliens from space invade Townsville, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls and all the children of Townsville to take a bite out of crime. Down N' Dirty: When Buttercup refuses to take a bath, the town kicks her out. But Buttercup decides to stick with her stink until her favorite thing is taken away from her.

removed.title: Twisted Sister/Cover Up
removed.description: Twisted Sister: The girls decide they need some help fighting crime so they create another Powerpuff Girl. But they don't get the combination of sugar, spice and everything nice quite right./Cover Up: Blossom and Bubbles learn that Buttercup has secretly been rubbing a security blanket before every battle to make herself a super fighter. Can the girls convince Buttercup that her strength is within?

removed.title: Jewel of the Aisle/Super Zeroes
removed.description: Jewel of the Isle: A crook hides a huge diamond in a box of the girls' favorite cereal. But how can he trick the girls into giving him some cereal in order to get the jewel back?/Super Zeroes: The girls don't think they have enough superhero accessories like those found in the comic books. They begin to emulate their favorite characters, complete with gadgets and gizmos.

removed.description: Imaginary Fiend: The new boy in school has a special friend nobody else can see. When this imaginary friend begins destroying the class, the girls must imagine how to stop him./Cootie Gras: Mojo observes that everyone is staying away from little Harry Pitt because he has cooties. So Mojo concocts a plan to keep the girls away by using this cootie-covered boy as bait.
